                <note xml:id="tnote.n18">1.10 I hear] <hi rend="italic">after del</hi> ‘which I trust will not [<hi rend="italic">interl pencil</hi>] cause you any [<hi rend="italic">altered from</hi> ‘no;’ <hi rend="italic">pencil</hi>] inconvenience.—’ </note>
